						<summary>

						<p>Slab set up in a field called ‘Hittalukōṭe’.</p>						

						<p>Mallikārjuna 1461 A.D.</p>						

						<p>This badly damaged record registers a gift of land when <hi rend="bold">Śaṅkaradēva-voḍeya</hi> was governing <hi rend="bold">Bārakūru-rājya</hi> under the orders of <hi rend="italic">mahāpradhāna</hi> <hi rend="bold">Rāmachandra-daṇṇāyakā.</hi> The details are all, however, lost.</p>						

						<p>It is dated <hi rend="bold">Śaka 1383, Vishu, Mārgaśira śu. 3, Thursday</hi> corresponding to <hi rend="bold">1461 A.D., November 5.</hi> </p>						

						</summary>
